<span style="line-height:1;"><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif;"><span style="font-size:12px;">{{!Account.billingcity}}, {{!Account.billingstatecode}} {{!Account.billingpostalcode}}</span></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif;"><span style="font-size:12px;"><br />
Dear {{!Account.first_name__c}},</span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif;"><span style="font-size:12px;">On behalf of the many patients we serve, thank you for your generous donation to the Icla da Silva Foundation.&nbsp;</span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif;"><span style="font-size:12px;">Your support will provide logistical, emotional, and critical financial support to remove barriers to treatment for patients with diseases whose only cure is a bone marrow or cord blood transplant.</span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif;"><span style="font-size:12px;">For those of us blessed with good health, it is difficult to imagine the value that hope can bring to someone whose life is in the hands of others.&nbsp; Thank you for contributing to the dream that one-day cancer and blood disorders will be a thing of the past.&nbsp; In the meantime, I want you to know that if it weren’t for compassionate and generous people like you, I don’t know those patients and family could cope with the critical challenges of treatment. So, thank you for your generous support.</span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif;"><span style="font-size:12px;"></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif;"><span style="font-size:12px;">You are a ray of light to those facing dark times.</span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif;"><span style="font-size:12px;">Warm regards,</span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif;"><span style="font-size:12px;"><br />
Airam da Silva, M.P.H.</span></span><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif;"><span style="font-size:12px;"><br />
President</span></span></p>
